caption.p: Characteristic high-resolution gas chromatography (HRGC) profiles of pumpkin ( C. maxima, var. Berrettina) seed oil samples. Margaric acid, 5. Heptadecenoic acid, 6. Stearic acid, 7. Oleic acid, 8. Linoleic acid, 9. Linolenic acid, 10. Arachidic acid, 11. Behenic acid, 12. Eicosenoic acid, 13. Lignoceric acid.
